∀ {P : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry.Plane P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ LineSegment P B C → Y ∈ LineSegment P C A → Z ∈ LineSegment P A B →
    Geometry.Area.triangle A Z Y ≤ Geometry.Area.triangle X Y Z ∨
    Geometry.Area.triangle B X Z ≤ Geometry.Area.triangle X Y Z ∨
    Geometry.Area.triangle C Y X ≤ Geometry.Area.triangle X Y Z

∀ {P : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ LineSegment ℝ B C → Y ∈ LineSegment ℝ C A → Z ∈ LineSegment ℝ A B →
    min (EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea A Z Y) (min (EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea B X Z) (EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea C Y X)) ≤
      EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea X Y Z

∀ {P : Type u_1} [inst : EuclideanGeometry P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ EuclideanGeometry.openSegment B C →
  Y ∈ EuclideanGeometry.openSegment C A →
  Z ∈ EuclideanGeometry.openSegment A B →
  min (EuclideanGeometry.area A Z Y)
      (min (EuclideanGeometry.area B X Z) (EuclideanGeometry.area C Y X)) ≤
  EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z

∀ {P : Type u_1} [inst : EuclideanGeometry P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  EuclideanGeometry.Collinear {B, C, X} →
  EuclideanGeometry.Collinear {C, A, Y} →
  EuclideanGeometry.Collinear {A, B, Z} →
  (EuclideanGeometry.area A Z Y ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z ∨
   EuclideanGeometry.area B X Z ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z ∨
   EuclideanGeometry.area C Y X ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z)

∀ {P : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry.Plane P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ EuclideanGeometry.lineSegment B C →
  Y ∈ EuclideanGeometry.lineSegment C A →
  Z ∈ EuclideanGeometry.lineSegment A B →
  min (EuclideanGeometry.area A Z Y) (min (EuclideanGeometry.area B X Z) (EuclideanGeometry.area C Y X)) ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z

∀ {P : Type u_1} [inst : EuclideanGeometry.Plane P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  EuclideanGeometry.Collinear {B, C, X} → EuclideanGeometry.Collinear {C, A, Y} → EuclideanGeometry.Collinear {A, B, Z} →
  min (EuclideanGeometry.area A Z Y) (min (EuclideanGeometry.area B X Z) (EuclideanGeometry.area C Y X)) ≤
  EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z

∀ {P : Type u} [inst : EuclideanSpace ℝ P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  ∃ (T : Finset (Fin 3 → P)), (T.card = 3 ∧ (∀ p ∈ T, p ∈ {X, Y, Z}) ∧
  ∑ p in T, EuclideanGeometry.area (p 0) (p 1) (p 2) ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z) → 
  EuclideanGeometry.area A Z Y ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z ∨ 
  EuclideanGeometry.area B X Z ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z ∨ 
  EuclideanGeometry.area C Y X ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z

∀ {P : Type} [inst : EuclideanGeometry P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ Segment B C → Y ∈ Segment C A → Z ∈ Segment A B →
  Area A Z Y ≤ Area X Y Z ∨ Area B X Z ≤ Area X Y Z ∨ Area C Y X ≤ Area X Y Z

∀ {P : Type} [inst : EuclideanSpace P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ OpenSegment ℝ B C → Y ∈ OpenSegment ℝ C A → Z ∈ OpenSegment ℝ A B →
  let area (p1 p2 p3 : P) := EuclideanGeometry.area ℝ p1 p2 p3 in
  area A Z Y ≤ area X Y Z ∨ area B X Z ≤ area X Y Z ∨ area C Y X ≤ area X Y Z

∀ {P : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry.Plane P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  EuclideanGeometry.Collinear {B, C, X} → EuclideanGeometry.Collinear {C, A, Y} → EuclideanGeometry.Collinear {A, B, Z} →
  (EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea A Z Y ≤ EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea X Y Z ∨
   EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea B X Z ≤ EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea X Y Z ∨
   EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea C Y X ≤ EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea X Y Z)
